# Vein Spiral — Cursor Rules

> Cursor가 자동으로 읽는 프로젝트 규칙입니다.  
> 전체 규칙 원본: `docs/UX_RULES.md`

## Stack

- Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript strict
- Tailwind v4, Supabase, custom UI (no shadcn/Radix/sonner)
- `cn()` from `@/lib/cn`

## 🔴 코드 규칙 (반드시 준수)

### Form Submit — ClientActionForm 필수
```tsx
// ❌ NEVER
<form action={fn}><button type="submit" /></form>

// ✅ ALWAYS
import { ClientActionForm } from '@/components/ui/client-action-form';
import { SubmitButton } from '@/components/ui/submit-button';

<ClientActionForm action={fn} successTitle="저장 완료" errorTitle="저장 실패">
  <SubmitButton>저장</SubmitButton>
</ClientActionForm>
```

### Destructive Actions — DangerActionButton 필수
```tsx
// ❌ NEVER: window.confirm(), alert(), raw button with onClick delete
// ✅ ALWAYS:
import { DangerActionButton } from '@/components/ui/danger-action-button';
<DangerActionButton
  action={deleteAction}
  fields={{ id }}
  title="삭제 확인"
  description="삭제하면 복구할 수 없습니다."
  highlightedInfo={`대상: ${name}`}
  confirmLabel="삭제"
  successTitle="삭제 완료"
/>
```

### Toast — useToast 필수
```tsx
import { useToast } from '@/components/ui/toast-provider';
const { success, error, undo } = useToast();
// 에러 메시지: 원인 + 해결방법 명시 필수 ("에러가 발생했습니다" 금지)
// 삭제 후: undo() 토스트로 8초 복구 옵션
```

### Button Rules
- Server components → `Button` from `@/components/ui/button`
- Client + tooltip/disabledReason → `EnhancedButton` from `@/components/ui/enhanced-button`
- **`button.tsx`에 `'use client'` 추가 금지** (서버 컴포넌트 호환)
- Loading state → `isLoading` prop 항상 사용

### Server Actions
- 성공 후 반드시 `revalidatePath()` 호출
- Optimistic update 적극 사용

### Accessibility
- 모든 인터랙티브 요소에 `aria-label` 또는 visible label
- 모달: focus trap + ESC 닫기
- 로딩 중: `aria-busy`, `aria-disabled`

## Component Paths

```
@/components/ui/client-action-form   → form wrapper + transition + toast
@/components/ui/danger-action-button → destructive action + confirm modal
@/components/ui/toast-provider       → useToast hook
@/components/ui/button               → base button (server-safe)
@/components/ui/enhanced-button      → button + tooltip (client only)
@/components/ui/submit-button        → form submit button
@/components/ui/loading              → LoadingOverlay, InlineLoadingSpinner
@/components/ui/inline-error         → error with cause + resolution
@/components/ui/confirmation-modal   → native <dialog> confirm modal
```

See full rules: `docs/UX_RULES.md`
